  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Safety and tolerability of rivastigmine for up to 52 weeks of treatment in patients with VaD and probable VaD</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>52 week's treatment with rivastigmine on cognition, activities of daily living, behavior and clinical staging in patients with VaD and probable VaD</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
